ies that can regenerate, accelerate, or spawn additional threats.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994940/extras/62d86ed19a66369438c7688e67bf1669.poster.avif?t=1722187371\" width=668 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994940/extras/62d86ed19a66369438c7688e67bf1669.webm?t=1722187371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994940/extras/62d86ed19a66369438c7688e67bf1669.mp4?t=1722187371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Endless Replayability: </strong>With a multitude of genetic enhancements and adaptive enemy tactics, each game offers new challenges and decisions, ensuring unique experiences with every playthrough.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994940/extras/24ec7d2064f7c93e44d395e3b0f86903.poster.avif?t=1722187371\" width=668 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994940/extras/24ec7d2064f7c93e44d395e3b0f86903.webm?t=1722187371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2994940/extras/24ec7d2064f7c93e44d395e3b0f86903.mp4?t=1722187371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Coming Soon:</strong> <u>Acquired immunity mechanics!!</u><br><br><strong>Support Independent Development</strong><br><br>As a solo developer not well-versed in the art of social media, I rely on the support of players like you. If you've enjoyed \"STEM Defense\", please help spread the word and make it known to others!",
